  "texts": [
    "To this end, we first selected a collection of 12 datasets, and empirically measure each dataset's quality by 1) sample upto 10k samples from each dataset, 2) train SFT-finetuned Gemma-2b and record its performance on MT-bench.",
    "We present the results in Figure A2 and Figure A3.",
    "We then used the top-six datasets according to their overall score in our offline preference learning experiments in Section 3.3.",
    "The baseline is our π SFT model.",
    "For all runs, we finetune from the best π SFT obtained from Section 3.2."
  ],
